flow.name: Signing Process
flow.BPMNXML:
<definitions targetNamespace="http://www.activiti.org/test" expressionLanguage="http://www.w3.org/1999/XPath" typeLanguage="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:omgdi="http://www.omg.org/spec/DD/20100524/DI" xmlns:omgdc="http://www.omg.org/spec/DD/20100524/DC" xmlns:bpmndi="http://www.omg.org/spec/BPMN/20100524/DI" xmlns:activiti="http://activiti.org/bpmn" xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xmlns="http://www.omg.org/spec/BPMN/20100524/MODEL">
  <message name="injectListJSON" id="injectListJSON"/>
  <process isExecutable="true" name="Signing Process" id="documentsign">
    <startEvent name="Start" id="startevent1"/>
    <endEvent name="End" id="endevent1"/>
    <userTask activiti:formKey="poi_select_form" activiti:assignee="${wf_currentAssignee}" name="Select Documents" id="form1"/>
    <serviceTask activiti:class="plugins.facts" name="Pull Shares" id="fact1">
      <extensionElements>
        <activiti:field name="PluginKey">
          <activiti:string>poi_SELECT_fact</activiti:string>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="parameterMap">
          <activiti:expression>${getMap}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
      </extensionElements>
    </serviceTask>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="fact1" sourceRef="startevent1" id="flow1"/>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="form1" sourceRef="fact1" id="flow2"/>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="servicetask1" sourceRef="form1" id="flow3"/>
    <boundaryEvent cancelActivity="false" attachedToRef="form1" name="Message" id="boundarymessage1">
      <messageEventDefinition messageRef="injectListJSON"/>
    </boundaryEvent>
    <serviceTask activiti:class="plugins.facts" name="Docusign Invoke" id="servicetask1">
      <extensionElements>
        <activiti:field name="PluginKey">
          <activiti:string>poi_SIGN_fact</activiti:string>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="parameterMap">
          <activiti:expression>${get2Map}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
      </extensionElements>
    </serviceTask>
    <userTask activiti:formKey="poi_sign_form" activiti:assignee="${wf_currentAssignee}" name="Sign Documents" id="usertask1"/>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="usertask1" sourceRef="servicetask1" id="flow4"/>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="endevent1" sourceRef="usertask1" id="flow5"/>
    <boundaryEvent cancelActivity="true" attachedToRef="usertask1" name="Message" id="boundarymessage2">
      <messageEventDefinition messageRef="injectListJSON"/>
    </boundaryEvent>
  </process>
  <bpmndi:BPMNDiagram id="BPMNDiagram_perftest">
    <bpmndi:BPMNPlane id="BPMNPlane_perftest" bpmnElement="perftest">
      <bpmndi:BPMNShape id="BPMNShape_startevent1" bpmnElement="startevent1">
        <omgdc:Bounds y="350.0" x="790.0" width="35.0" height="35.0"/>
      </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
      <bpmndi:BPMNShape id="BPMNShape_endevent1" bpmnElement="endevent1">
        <omgdc:Bounds y="350.0" x="1500.0" width="35.0" height="35.0"/>
      </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
      <bpmndi:BPMNShape id="BPMNShape_form1" bpmnElement="form1">
        <omgdc:Bounds y="340.0" x="1040.0" width="105.0" height="55.0"/>
      </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
      <bpmndi:BPMNShape id="BPMNShape_fact1" bpmnElement="fact1">
        <omgdc:Bounds y="340.0" x="890.0" width="105.0" height="55.0"/>
      </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
      <bpmndi:BPMNShape id="BPMNShape_boundarymessage1" bpmnElement="boundarymessage1">
        <omgdc:Bounds y="380.0" x="1116.0" width="30.0" height="30.0"/>
      </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
      <bpmndi:BPMNShape id="BPMNShape_servicetask1" bpmnElement="servicetask1">
        <omgdc:Bounds y="340.0" x="1190.0" width="105.0" height="55.0"/>
      </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
      <bpmndi:BPMNShape id="BPMNShape_usertask1" bpmnElement="usertask1">
        <omgdc:Bounds y="340.0" x="1330.0" width="105.0" height="55.0"/>
      </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
      <bpmndi:BPMNShape id="BPMNShape_boundarymessage2" bpmnElement="boundarymessage2">
        <omgdc:Bounds y="380.0" x="1416.0" width="30.0" height="30.0"/>
      </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
      <bpmndi:BPMNEdge id="BPMNEdge_flow1" bpmnElement="flow1">
        <omgdi:waypoint y="367.0" x="825.0"/>
        <omgdi:waypoint y="367.0" x="890.0"/>
      </bpmndi:BPMNEdge>
      <bpmndi:BPMNEdge id="BPMNEdge_flow2" bpmnElement="flow2">
        <omgdi:waypoint y="367.0" x="995.0"/>
        <omgdi:waypoint y="367.0" x="1040.0"/>
      </bpmndi:BPMNEdge>
      <bpmndi:BPMNEdge id="BPMNEdge_flow3" bpmnElement="flow3">
        <omgdi:waypoint y="367.0" x="1145.0"/>
        <omgdi:waypoint y="367.0" x="1190.0"/>
      </bpmndi:BPMNEdge>
      <bpmndi:BPMNEdge id="BPMNEdge_flow4" bpmnElement="flow4">
        <omgdi:waypoint y="367.0" x="1295.0"/>
        <omgdi:waypoint y="367.0" x="1330.0"/>
      </bpmndi:BPMNEdge>
      <bpmndi:BPMNEdge id="BPMNEdge_flow5" bpmnElement="flow5">
        <omgdi:waypoint y="367.0" x="1435.0"/>
        <omgdi:waypoint y="367.0" x="1500.0"/>
      </bpmndi:BPMNEdge>
    </bpmndi:BPMNPlane>
  </bpmndi:BPMNDiagram>
</definitions>

        </activiti:field>

    <serviceTask id="task5" name="Read Record Again" activiti:class="plugins.fact_components.api_APIdocShare_Read_Obj_toFields">
      <extensionElements>
        <activiti:field name="objType">
          <activiti:expression>${objTypeId}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="objKey">
          <activiti:expression>${objId}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
      </extensionElements>
    </serviceTask>
    <exclusiveGateway id="exclusivegateway1" name="Exclusive Gateway" default="default"></exclusiveGateway>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow12" name="GETOBJS" sourceRef="exclusivegateway1" targetRef="task1">
      <conditionExpression xsi:type="tFormalExpression"><![CDATA[${apidata_method == "GETOBJS"}]]></conditionExpression>
    </sequenceFlow>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow13" name="GETRECS" sourceRef="exclusivegateway1" targetRef="task2">
      <conditionExpression xsi:type="tFormalExpression"><![CDATA[${apidata_method == "GETRECS"}]]></conditionExpression>
    </sequenceFlow>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow14" name="GET" sourceRef="exclusivegateway1" targetRef="task3">
      <conditionExpression xsi:type="tFormalExpression"><![CDATA[${apidata_method == "GET"}]]></conditionExpression>
    </sequenceFlow>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow15" name="PUT" sourceRef="exclusivegateway1" targetRef="task4">
      <conditionExpression xsi:type="tFormalExpression"><![CDATA[${apidata_method == "PUT" || apidata_method == "PATCH"}]]></conditionExpression>
    </sequenceFlow>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow16" sourceRef="task5" targetRef="endevent1"></sequenceFlow>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow17" sourceRef="task3" targetRef="endevent1"></sequenceFlow>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow18" sourceRef="task2" targetRef="endevent1"></sequenceFlow>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow19" sourceRef="task1" targetRef="endevent1"></sequenceFlow>
    <sequenceFlow id="default" name="Unsupported" sourceRef="exclusivegateway1" targetRef="endevent1"></sequenceFlow>
    <userTask id="usertask1" name="Default" activiti:formKey="poi_default_view"></userTask>
    <userTask id="usertask2" name="Shares" activiti:formKey="poi_shareslist_view"></userTask>
    <userTask id="usertask3" name="Preview" activiti:formKey="poi_preview_view"></userTask>
